'''Anders Indset''' (born 11 April 1978) is a Norwegian [[philosopher]], [[author]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.wild-knowledge.com|title=Wild Knowledge - Outthink the Revolution {{!}} The book "WILD KNOWLEDGE - Outthink the Revolution" by Business Philosopher Anders Indset|website=www.wild-knowledge.com|language=en-GB|access-date=2017-03-21}}</ref> and [[Public speaking|public speaker]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chartwellspeakers.com/speaker/anders-indset/|title=Anders Indset {{!}} Business Philosopher & Speaker {{!}} Chartwell|work=Expert Keynote and Motivational Speakers {{!}} Chartwell Speakers|access-date=2017-03-09|language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://frontrowspeakers.com/speakers/anders-indset|title=Anders Indset — Front Row Speakers|website=frontrowspeakers.com|language=en|access-date=2017-03-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://premium-speakers.de/eng/speaker/anders-indset|title=Speaker Anders Indset book|website=premium-speakers.de|language=en|access-date=2017-03-09}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.lidspeakers.com/speakers/anders-indset/|title=Anders Indset - LID Speakers|work=LID Speakers|access-date=2017-03-09|language=en-GB}}</ref>

He is a visiting guest lecturer at leading international business schools, a co-founder of FIA <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.frankfurtinternationalalliance.com/de/frankfurt-expert/anders-indset/|title=Anders Indset » FIA {{!}} Frankfurt International Alliance|work=FIA {{!}} Frankfurt International Alliance|access-date=2017-03-09|language=de-DE}}</ref> and an advisory board member of GTEC - [[German Tech Entrepreneurship Center]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://gtec.center|title=GTEC {{!}} German Tech Entrepreneurship Center|website=gtec.center|language=en-US|access-date=2017-03-09}}</ref> He is currently based in [[Frankfurt]], [[Germany]].

